defaultQ107default 
defaultChair:default 
defaultOn that point, Mr Lambert,
default we have seen figures that the value in 
defaultWales
default alone could be £70 billion. Trying to bring this down into figures that people relate to, is it the case that, if we can tap into this resource, gas prices will fall, as they have in the 
defaultUnited States
